Package org.apache.jena.rdfxml.xmlinput.impl

Class XMLHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
      • org.apache.jena.rdfxml.xmlinput.impl.XMLHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ARPErrorNumbers, Names, org.xml.sax.ContentHandler, org.xml.sax.DTDHandler, org.xml.sax.EntityResolver, org.xml.sax.ErrorHandler, org.xml.sax.ext.LexicalHandler
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RDFXMLParser, SAX2RDFImpl
    public class XMLHandler
extends org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
implements ARPErrorNumbers, Names
    This class converts SAX events into a stream of encapsulated events suitable for the RDF parser. In effect, this is the RDF lexer. updates by kers to handle exporting namespace prefix maps.
